            )
URL: https://github.com/MikkoVihtakari/ggOceanPlots
BugReports: https://github.com/MikkoVihtakari/ggOceanPlots/issues
Description: Provides tools to determine water masses from salinity and
  temperature data. Contains temperature-salinity (TS) and section plots
  that can be expanded using 'ggplot2'. The package has currently been
  tuned for the Svalbard region.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
